    {
      "id": "PopularPost335470",
      "post_content": "I love this card, for a while until **[Quicksilver Geyser](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Quicksilver Geyser)** and **[Whiplash Trap](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Whiplash Trap)** was introduced, this was the only card that gets rid of fast growing creature decks that outpaces **[Boomerang](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Boomerang)**. **[echoing truth](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=echoing truth)** is too situational to benefit 2+ returns and sometimes your creatures can get caught up too!  \n  \nThis was a favorite hard counter to re-animator decks. Let them use 3+ cards to bring that [Phantom Nishoba](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Phantom Nishoba) and [Visara the Dreadful](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Visara the Dreadful) and then use this card to see their biggest sad face LOL  \n  \nThe only drawback is sorcery speed but I think that's fair.",
      "posted_by": "RockstarSnorlax",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost335470\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">I love this card, for a while until <b><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Quicksilver Geyser\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Quicksilver Geyser\">Quicksilver Geyser</a></b> and <b><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Whiplash Trap\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Whiplash Trap\">Whiplash Trap</a></b> was introduced, this was the only card that gets rid of fast growing creature decks that outpaces <b><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Boomerang\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Boomerang\">Boomerang</a></b>. <b><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"echoing truth\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=echoing truth\">echoing truth</a></b> is too situational to benefit 2+ returns and sometimes your creatures can get caught up too!<br/><br/>This was a favorite hard counter to re-animator decks. Let them use 3+ cards to bring that <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Phantom Nishoba\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Phantom Nishoba\">Phantom Nishoba</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Visara the Dreadful\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Visara the Dreadful\">Visara the Dreadful</a> and then use this card to see their biggest sad face LOL<br/><br/>The only drawback is sorcery speed but I think that's fair.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '335470'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy100950\">RockstarSnorlax</span>\r\n                                (8/18/2013 8:12:48 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
